                                   <p>The Jesuit Refugee Service (JRS) is an international Catholic organisation with a mission to accompany, serve and advocate on behalf of refugees and other forcibly displaced persons. JRS undertakes services at national and regional levels with the support of an international office in Rome. Founded in November 1980 as a work of the Society of Jesus, JRS w...  

        <br />
    <a href="/jobs-at/jesuit-refugee-service-jrs" class="view-all2" style="margin-top:0px">Read more about this company</a>
